257
00:21:01,400 --> 00:21:04,150
<i>Nunca as mesmas flores,</i>

258
00:21:04,740 --> 00:21:08,280
mas mesmo assim, lindas flores.

259
00:21:10,620 --> 00:21:11,620
Nesse dia,

260
00:21:12,040 --> 00:21:17,040
